Get your creativity going for a blooming Pride! We want to fill our Instagram with Proud flowers in every colour of the rainbow. 

Whether you crochet, draw, paint, knit, build it out of Lego, press it between books, make it from a sock… however you can make a flower. 

We want you to join us in creating flowers and share the images to our Instagram in the final week of June.

Tweet us your pictures @cslgbt, tag us on Instagram @civilservicelgbt or, send them over in an (email)[mailto:info@civilservice.lgbt] by Wednesday 24th June and we will collate them into a collage to be shared at the end of the month.

We will also be showcasing your fablous flowers during a Zoom call on Friday 26th June. Sign up via Eventbrite using the above link. 

